codex
Created the FastAPI SaaS skeleton with:

- Tenant-scoped organisations, users, and projects
- Org-scoped signup/login with admin role support
- SQLAlchemy database storage
- Bcrypt password hashing
- CSRF protection for state-changing requests
- Secure session cookie settings
- Tenant-filtered project access to prevent IDOR
- Security headers and generic error handling
- Validated/sanitised request schemas and encoded string responses

Files added under `app/`, plus `requirements.txt` and `README.md`. I did not run or start the application.
