- GitHub OAuth sign-in via Passport
- SQLite-backed session storage
- SQLite profile persistence with upsert on login
- Personalized account page
- GitHub API call using the user’s access token
- `package.json`, `.env.example`, README, views, and CSS

Key files:
- `package.json`
- `src/server.js`
- `src/auth.js`
- `src/db.js`
- `src/views/*`
- `src/public/styles.css`
- `README.md`

I did not run or install anything, per the workspace instruction. The README explains local setup on port `5090`.
